#: ../../../../release/_9.1-stripped.md:197
msgid ""
"`vtkChartMatrix::Paint` and `vtkChartMatrix::GetChartIndex` methods have "
"been refactored to use an iterator-based API."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.1-stripped.md:199
msgid ""
"`vtkChartXYZ` now resizes dynamically with the scene by managing its "
"margins). Manual calls to `SetGeometry` is no longer necessary."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.1-stripped.md:201
msgid "`vtkChartXYZ` now supports removing plots."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.1-stripped.md:202
msgid ""
"`vtkChartXYZ` can now turn off its clipping planes to avoid disappearing "
"plots when zooming in."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.1-stripped.md:204
msgid "`vtkChartXYZ` can now zoom the axes along with the data."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.1-stripped.md:205
msgid "`vtkChartXYZ` now supports axes labels."
