msgid "Web {#web}"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.1-stripped.md:567
msgid ""
"`render_window_serializer.py` now supports serialization of a "
"`vtkRenderWindow` that contains `vtkVolume`, `vtkVolumeProperty`, or "
"`vtkVolumeMapper`."
msgstr ""

