"template instantiations are split into separate TU compilations."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.1-stripped.md:641
msgid ""
"The `VTK_TARGET_SPECIFIC_COMPONENTS` option may be specified to provide "
"target-specific installation components."
msgstr ""

