"`VTK_USE_VIDEO_FOR_WINDOWS_CAPTURE`, but the old name is given for "
"compatibility."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.1-stripped.md:719
msgid ""
"`vtkUnicodeString` and `vtkUnicodeStringArray` are now deprecated since VTK, "
"since 8.2, has assumed UTF-8 for all string APIs. As such, "
"`vtkUnicodeString` and `vtkUnicodeStringArray` did not provide any "
"additional information. Users which used them to convert UTF-8 to UCS-2 for "
"Windows API usages should instead use `VTK::vtksys`'s `SystemTools` APIs for "
"converting such strings."
